(95, 'Up or Down on Ethereum in next 4 hours?', 'Ethereum-updown-four_hours-17740944034406', 'If the price of Ethereum is above 2157.43 after 4 hours, \"Yes\" wins. If it is below, \"No\" wins. Results will be based on the price at 2026-03-21 16:00:03. Winning result based on the bybit price feed.', 3, 2, 6, NULL, 2157.43, '2026-03-21 12:00:03', '2026-03-21 16:00:03', 'resolved', 'yes', 1.00, 'uploads/coins/eth.svg', 'four_hours', 1, 2, 938.56, 0.4, 0.6, '2026-03-21 12:00:03', '2026-03-23 08:00:10'),
