(104, 'Will it rain in Tamil Nadu on April 1, 2026?', 'will-it-rain-in-tamil-nadu-on', 'Resolution based on India Meteorological Department data\r\n“Rain” = ≥ 0.1 mm recorded precipitation\r\nTime window: 00:00–23:59 IST\r\nIf data unavailable → fallback to AccuWeather or Weather.com', 10, 12, 15, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'open', NULL, 1.00, 'uploads/question/named-storm-before-2025-atlantic-hurricane-season.svg', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, 0.5, 0.5, '2026-03-24 08:50:13', '2026-03-24 08:50:13'),
